# 1️⃣ Expired Service Principal Secret Broke CI/CD

### Incident

Deployment pipelines suddenly failed.

```
AADSTS7000215: Invalid client secret
```

### Root Cause

Service Principal secret expired.

### Example

Azure DevOps pipeline authenticating Azure.

### Fix

Rotate secret.

```bash
az ad sp credential reset --name <app-id>
```

### Prevention

Use **certificate authentication instead of secrets**.

---

# 2️⃣ Production AKS Access Failure

### Incident

Engineers could not access production Kubernetes cluster.

### Root Cause

RBAC misconfiguration between **AKS and Azure AD**.

### Fix

Reconfigure cluster RBAC.

```bash
az aks update \
--resource-group prod-rg \
--name prod-aks \
--enable-aad
```

### Lesson

Always test **AAD RBAC integration** in staging.

---

# 3️⃣ Conditional Access Blocked DevOps Automation

### Incident

Terraform deployment suddenly failed.

### Root Cause

Conditional Access policy required MFA.

Automation cannot complete MFA.

### Fix

Exclude service principals.

```
Conditional Access → Exclude workload identity
```

---

# 4️⃣ Expired Certificate in App Registration

### Incident

Internal microservice authentication stopped working.

### Root Cause

Expired certificate in **App Registration**.

### Fix

Upload new certificate.

```
Entra ID
→ App Registrations
→ Certificates & Secrets
```

### Prevention

Enable **certificate expiration alerts**.

---

# 5️⃣ Massive Login Failures Across Organization

### Incident

Thousands of users unable to login.

### Root Cause

DNS issue affecting login endpoint.

Example:

```
login.microsoftonline.com unreachable
```

### Fix

Network team fixed DNS resolution.

### Lesson

Always monitor **identity endpoints**.

---

# 6️⃣ Unauthorized Resource Creation

### Incident

Unexpected VMs created in subscription.

### Root Cause

Compromised credentials of DevOps engineer.

### Fix

Immediate actions:

1. Disable account
2. Rotate credentials
3. Audit activity logs

### Prevention

Use **Privileged Identity Management (PIM)**.

---

# 7️⃣ Azure DevOps Service Connection Failure

### Incident

Pipeline error:

```
Failed to obtain access token
```

### Root Cause

Deleted service principal.

### Fix

Recreate service principal.

```bash
az ad sp create-for-rbac
```

---

# 8️⃣ Key Vault Access Denied

### Incident

Application unable to retrieve secrets.

### Root Cause

Managed identity missing permission.

### Fix

```bash
az keyvault set-policy \
--name prod-kv \
--object-id <identity-id> \
--secret-permissions get list
```

---

# 9️⃣ Azure AD Sync Failure (Hybrid Identity)

### Incident

New users not appearing in Azure.

### Root Cause

Sync stopped in **Azure AD Connect**.

### Fix

Restart service.

```powershell
Start-Service ADSync
```

